  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6463205/" class="title-link">修身齐家与治国平天下</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6463205"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/yican/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2129048-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/yican/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">红皇后</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-12-16"
      class="main-meta">2013-12-16 10:55:49</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6463205_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  如果说成长会给人带来好处，那么我想唯一的好处就是明白了世间的道理。  小时候的我们，可能会无意识的诵读：予独爱莲之出淤泥而不染，濯清涟而不妖，中通外直，不蔓不枝，香远益清，亭亭净植....但是只有长大以后，我们才会明白出淤泥而不染是一种多么难以达到的人生状态，我...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/6463205/#comments">(5回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">31有用 / 1没用</span>
