  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6459604">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6459604/" class="title-link">做一个仁德谦恭的人</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6459604"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/anqiao0706/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1451157-14.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/anqiao0706/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">飞鱼</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-12-13"
      class="main-meta">2013-12-13 14:31:57</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6459604_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  用作者梁先生的话来说，没有读过《群书治要》是一种人生遗憾，很遗憾，我没有读过。可是我庆幸的是，在我成长的过程中，老爸的言传身教已经将书中的一些智慧告诉了我。所以，翻开这本书，细细读来特别的亲切，又仿佛回到那样的时刻，老爸语重心长讲述那些人生大道理，引经据典...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">8有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
